Creators of the mega-popular Netflix series Stranger Things, the Duffer brothers, were pretty tight-lipped about season 3 of the popular show, but they did confirm one major detail &ndash; there will be a<span style="color: red;"> time jump</span>.<br />
<br />
It makes sense that there will be a time jump between the second and third season if only for the fact that the young cast is growing up so quickly. &quot;The kids are growing up. It would be a little silly if we just started right after this ended because they look so old, already just seeing them here I'm like, 'Oh my god.' They just grow so fast,&quot;
